<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3779800>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Dorsal (A and B) and ventral (C and D) views of host newts from which the type specimens of Hygrobates salamandrarum were collected. Figure A and C show the mature male. Photos were provided by Arne Lindau. Scale shows 10mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3779800/files/figure.png" ;
